title: Open Weekends For Tour-Newly Renovated-Luxury Amenities-Great Location
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-The Event Features a Demonstration Kitchen with Enough Room to Entertain a Few Close Friends or a Crowd', '-Large, private balcony with panoramic views', '-Concrete construction creates acoustically sound units', '-Extra stuff?', 'Convenient Storage Lockers Available', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Pet Friendly Featuring Pet Spa and Bark Park', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', '-Moen Align bathroom collection in a chrome finish for a modern look', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
